### ============================================================================
### MULTI-TENANT PM SAAS - CORE API TESTS
### Onboarding Requests (Future Feature)
### ============================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Variables
@adminSessionToken = your-admin-session-token-here
@onboardingRequestId = your-request-id-here

### ============================================================================
### CREATE ONBOARDING REQUEST
### ============================================================================

### Submit Onboarding Request (During Signup)
# @name submitOnboarding
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/onboarding
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyName": "Acme Corporation",
  "companyWebsite": "https://acme.com",
  "industry": "Technology",
  "companySize": "MEDIUM",
  "businessType": "B2B SaaS",
  "useCase": "We need project management for our development teams",
  "expectedEmployees": 25,
  "expectedProjects": 50,
  "interestedFeatures": ["Task Management", "Time Tracking", "Reports"],
  "additionalInfo": "We're migrating from Jira and need data import support"
}

### ============================================================================
### LIST ONBOARDING REQUESTS (Admin Only)
### ============================================================================

### Get All Onboarding Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/onboarding
Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{adminSessionToken}}

### Get Pending Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/onboarding?status=PENDING
Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{adminSessionToken}}

### Get Reviewed Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/onboarding?status=REVIEWED
Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{adminSessionToken}}

### ============================================================================
### ONBOARDING REQUEST DETAILS
### ============================================================================

### Get Request by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/onboarding/{{onboardingRequestId}}
Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{adminSessionToken}}

### ============================================================================
### REVIEW ONBOARDING REQUEST (Admin)
### ============================================================================

### Mark as Reviewed with Notes
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/onboarding/{{onboardingRequestId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{adminSessionToken}}

{
  "status": "REVIEWED",
  "reviewNotes": "Good fit for Premium tier. Contacted via email to discuss data migration.",
  "recommendedTier": "PREMIUM"
}

### ============================================================================
### NOTES
### ============================================================================

# Onboarding Flow:
# 1. User signs up and fills out onboarding form
# 2. Request submitted with status=PENDING
# 3. Admin reviews request and contacts user
# 4. Admin approves tenant with appropriate tier based on needs
# 5. Request marked as REVIEWED

# Use Cases:
# - Collect business information during signup
# - Help admins decide appropriate subscription tier
# - Understand customer needs for better support
# - Sales qualified leads (SQL) identification
# - Custom enterprise tier negotiations

# Company Size Options:
# - SMALL: 1-50 employees
# - MEDIUM: 51-200 employees
# - LARGE: 201-1000 employees
# - ENTERPRISE: 1000+ employees
